elvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">在现场最外端，设置急救车停放点，如遇突发事件可第一时间开出。</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"paragraph text-align-type-left pap-line-1.3 pap-line-rule-auto pap-spacing-before-3pt pap-spacing-after-3pt\" style=\"line-height: 130%; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px;\"><br></p><ol start=\"2\" type=\"1\"><li data-id=\"bmzj4j\" data-level=\"0\" data-level-text=\"%1.\" data-order=\"1\" data-format=\"STNumberFormat_decimal\" data-type=\"Numbered\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; padding-left: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"paragraph text-align-type-left pap-line-1.7 pap-line-rule-auto pap-spacing-before-0pt pap-spacing-after-0pt pap-left-indent-16.8pt pap-hanging-indent-16.8pt tco-title-heading 3\" style=\"line-height: 170%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">现场人员情绪控制</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3></li></ol><ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"><li data-id=\"czo8hg\" data-level=\"0\" data-level-text=\"¡\" data-order=\"0\" data-format=\"STNumberFormat_bullet\" data-type=\"Bullet\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; padding-left: 0px;\"><p class=\"paragraph text-align-type-left pap-line-1.5 pap-line-rule-auto pap-spacing-before-0pt pap-spacing-after-0pt pap-left-indent-16.8pt pap-hanging-indent-16.8pt\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">活动现场如发生来宾对组织方不满而大声吵闹，现场工作人员应做到不计对错首先道歉，工作人员不许围观，尽量将来宾请至活动现场外或办公室内进行调解，调解人员人数原则上不超过两人(调解人员越多，来宾吵闹的情绪越高），为避免事态扩大，可适当满足来宾一些不合理的要求；</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p></li><li data-id=\"czo8hg\" data-level=\"0\" data-level-text=\"¡\" data-order=\"1\" data-format=\"STNumberFormat_bullet\" data-type=\"Bullet\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; padding-left: 0px;\"><p class=\"paragraph text-align-type-left pap-line-1.5 pap-line-rule-auto pap-spacing-before-0pt pap-spacing-after-0pt pap-left-indent-16.8pt pap-hanging-indent-16.8pt\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">无论遇到任何突发情况，工作人员原则上均需做到不大声叫喊、不乱跑动。</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"paragraph text-align-type-left pap-line-1.3 pap-line-rule-auto pap-spacing-before-3pt pap-spacing-after-3pt\" style=\"line-height: 130%; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px;\"><br></p><ol start=\"3\" type=\"1\"><li data-id=\"bmzj4j\" data-level=\"0\" data-level-text=\"%1.\" data-order=\"2\" data-fo