, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; padding-left: 0px;\"><p class=\"paragraph text-align-type-left pap-line-1.5 pap-line-rule-auto pap-spacing-before-0pt pap-spacing-after-0pt pap-left-indent-16.8pt pap-hanging-indent-16.8pt\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">尽量协调工程部门，仪式活动当天停止施工，避免超负荷跳闸。</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p></li><li data-id=\"3s5s63\" data-level=\"0\" data-level-text=\"¡\" data-order=\"2\" data-format=\"STNumberFormat_bullet\" data-type=\"Bullet\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; padding-left: 0px;\"><p class=\"paragraph text-align-type-left pap-line-1.5 pap-line-rule-auto pap-spacing-before-0pt pap-spacing-after-0pt pap-left-indent-16.8pt pap-hanging-indent-16.8pt\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">在配电柜处安排专业电工留守，一旦出现断电情况，可以第一时间进行处理，查明并解决电源问题后方可逐一启动各电子器材。</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p></li><li data-id=\"3s5s63\" data-level=\"0\" data-level-text=\"¡\" data-order=\"3\" data-format=\"STNumberFormat_bullet\" data-type=\"Bullet\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuan